  <data key="d1">Definition</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
  <data key="d3">We consider an autoregressive Transformer decoder. Let h ℓ t ∈ R d denote the hidden state at layer ℓ and position t . For each attention head, keys and values are computed as linear projections of the hidden states,</data>
